Class MainMenuView

java.lang.Object
javafx.scene.Node
javafx.scene.Parent
com.gr15.pacman.view.screen.BaseView
com.gr15.pacman.view.screen.MainMenuView
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
public class MainMenuView extends BaseView
Represents the main menu view of the application, containing UI elements such as buttons for starting a new game, and exiting. This view extends BaseView and lays out the buttons vertically centered using a VBox.
